Package: MGC
Type: Package
Title: The Multiscale Generalized Correlation (MGC) Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cencheng Shen, Eric Bridgeford, and Shangsi Wang
Maintainer: The package maintainer <cshen6@jhu.edu>
Description: Implements a number of data exploration tasks based on MGC: 
    computing the correlation measure, test independence via MGC and permutation test,
    k-sample test via MGC and permutation test (tba), feature screening via MGC (tba). 
    Applicable to Euclidean data, distance matrices, graphs (tba). Contains extensions
    to discriminability.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.1),
    SDMTools
Imports:
  ggplot2,
  reshape2,
  Rmisc,
  stats
Suggests: testthat,
  knitr,
  rmarkdown
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
